{"tid":620992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港獨派另辦集會　數十人出席","createTime":"2018-04-08T02:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T07:38:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b20e71b706c6c594f4d8a7381f23a79d54eaa2","tid":620992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355324&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCCtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c026ccea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355324&h=d204f3e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355324</a><br />\n<br />\n港獨派另辦集會　數十人出席<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180408/large/0407kaho4101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180408%2Flarge%2F0407kaho4101.jpg&h=7e39ffb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主張港獨的香港民族陣綫昨晚同時在立法會大樓外舉辦集會。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派在立法會示威區舉辦集會聲援港大學者戴耀廷的同時，主張港獨的香港民族陣綫亦同時在立法會大樓外舉辦集會，聲稱支持戴耀廷和言論自由，但只有數十人參加。香港民族陣綫召集人阿南稱，縱使他未必認同戴的行為，但仍會誓死捍衞戴的發言權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n少年被帶上警車<br />\n<br />\n香港民族陣綫昨晚的集會，與民主派集會同一時間，不過地點在立法會大樓外的添美道行人路上，集會開始前已有警員在場戒備，不時截查參與者，而集會期間，更有一名少年被帶上警車，最終整個集會約有40至50人參與。<br />\n<br />\n阿南表示，舉辦今集會主要是有兩點訴求，一方面希望表達獨派捍衞言論自由和學術自由的決心，另一方面亦向其他因主張港獨而被迫害的人顯示，獨派願意繼續支持他們，他解釋未有參與民主派集會，是因為與民主派在意識形態上有分歧，但在今次戴耀廷事件中，雙方立場一致，會誓死捍衞戴的發言權，又指今次對戴的批鬥，與《基本法》23條立法不無關係，認為若港人不為戴耀廷遇到的迫害發聲，那麼，「中共就可以有一個合理推測，預期當他日立23條嘅時候，香港人嘅反彈會比預期中細，咁有機會加速23條嘅立法」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t參加者：危機逼近不能麻木<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t譚耀宗抹黑戴組織港獨工作<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t中大學生會前幹事被拒入境澳門<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t【蘋果照相機】為言論自由打氣！<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t二千人集會撐戴耀廷李柱銘藉防波堤籲團結「大家蹺埋先有實力」<br />\n頭條 4小時前"},{"pid":"edccb4e2dbba74df781e51117065a7ff75b5564b","tid":620992,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fbc71474b59be82345862b53c5b3780c702e747","tid":620992,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"上兩年三千人<br />\n今年幾十人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c00546b1a15db134e723335da5b80752cc0f13a","tid":620992,"uid":117786,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:44:10.000Z","msg":"人多勢眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中共腳軟瀨屎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cabb686368ef71f2d391eadbf27ed552ae63ba0","tid":620992,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ba3e04c392a6d879eb0fd394b43738970e74cf","tid":620992,"uid":90863,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"好疊馬"},{"pid":"de184e90a29d51cc616803b0aab7bdba5c25127c","tid":620992,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"毒果 飯民喉舌唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb8f85fb557eb8ad8954adad4882c5063c1eed2","tid":620992,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"港獨派集會post竟然全部係負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0e56e034d927f1f1a2e9d8cfe51fdf233c41b1","tid":620992,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fb8f85fb557eb8ad8954adad4882c5063c1eed2","tid":620992,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dis